HB 595 Original 2026 Regular Session Jacob Landry
Abstract: Prohibits local governing authorities from actions that impede the state's ability
to develop natural resources including additional permitting requirements.
Proposed law provides that the dept. is vested with exclusive authority over the natural
resources of the state and prohibits local governing authorities from taking actions, including
requiring permits, affecting this subject matter.
(Adds R.S. 30:4.4)
